This is README file for Algorithm PA#1
Author: HsuanYu CHOU
Date: 2021-10-23
=====
SYNOPSIS:

NTU_sort -[IS|MS|QS|HS] <input_file_name> <output_file_name>

# This program supports four different sorting methods: insertion sort, merge sort, quicksort, and heapsort.

DIRECTORY:

bin/ executable binary
doc/ reports
lib/ library
src/ source C++ codes
======
HOW TO CIMPILE:

    make

======
HOW TO RUN:

    ./bin/NTU_sort -[IS|MS|QS|HS] <input_file_name> <output_file_name>

    For example,
    under hychou_pa1/
    ./bin/NTU_sort -HS inputs/1000000.case1.in outputs/1000000.case1.out

======
HOW TO VERIFY RESULT

    diff <output_file> <answer_file>

    For example,
    under hychou_pa1/
    diff outputs/1000000.case1.out inputs/1000000.case2.in
